Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「哔咔咔咔」的声音 发信源是这台装置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「哔哔—噗—」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那个装置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理看不见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请询问GEJI姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,访问确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换至GEJI姐模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在这里的机器到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是EGI系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EGI？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定期向宇宙发送特定频率声音的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过口袋电脑就可以听见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说君岛孝打算在这个岛上做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君岛孝是怎么死的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是被谋杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被谋杀的？被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相关资料已被删除
