Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frau 好像有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不理睬的话不太好哦
